Source: paper
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Build-Depends: dpkg-dev (>= 1.16.1~), debhelper (>= 9), cdbs (>=0.4.93~)

Package: paper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, paper-bin
Description: Paper sizes catalogue and utility
 The paper utility automates recognition of many different paper types
 and sizes for programs that need to print.

Package: paper-bin
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Paper sizes catalogue and utility (binaries)
 The paper utility automates recognition of many different paper types
 and sizes for programs that need to deal with printed output.
 .
 This package contains architecture-specific binaries.
